# 1Ô∏è‚É£ Required Software / Tools

All team members must install the following:

## Backend
- ‚úÖ Go (1.21+)
- ‚úÖ PostgreSQL (recommended)
  OR
- ‚úÖ Docker (optional alternative for DB)

## Frontend
- ‚úÖ Node.js (LTS version)
- ‚úÖ npm (comes with Node)

## Development Tools
- ‚úÖ VS Code
- ‚úÖ Git
- ‚úÖ Postman (for API testing)

